Package: dacx
Version: 0.5.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libmpv2 | libmpv1, libc6
Maintainer: BurntToasters <dacx@run.rosie>
Homepage: https://github.com/BurntToasters/Dacx
Description: Quick, lightweight cross-platform media player
 Dacx is a desktop media player built with Flutter and libmpv.
 Supports audio and video playback with drag-and-drop, minimal UI,
 and cross-platform consistency.
